u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Mi7-_GNVEn0?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Elol. im still laughing \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E haha. never tried it in space. to be honest if ksp would have any real physix it wouldnt do anything in the space but well.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AppleDavidJeans","CreatedById":84275,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-10T23:18:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI call witchcraft.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EJk this looks great. Good work man!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tuareg","CreatedById":84241,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-01T17:53:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ebug fixed: electricity consumption in .cfg should work now properly\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Eadded own shader for a fun effect (effect colors and size also in the .cfg)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/TpSSnbpW1mg?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-02-01T17:55:51Z\u0022 title=\u002202/01/2015 05:55  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 1, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by Tuareg\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GreatWyrmGold","CreatedById":107272,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-16T17:11:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tuareg\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Tuareg\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Elol. im still laughing \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E haha. never tried it in space. to be honest if ksp would have any real physix it wouldnt do anything in the space but well.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EActually, the problem has something to do with the way you coded the mod. I\u0027d bet real money that the anti-gravity room changes the magnitude of gravitational acceleration but not the direction. Thus, the room was being pulled more or less than the contents, causing relative motion.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EAnd if there were real physix it wouldn\u0027t do anything on the ground, either.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"falken","CreatedById":17316,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-16T17:15:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis kind of reminds me of the Neutral Buoyancy lab!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Linear","CreatedById":26619,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-16T17:29:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELike it a lot!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"hieywiey","CreatedById":99098,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-17T23:28:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EGive it to Danny2462! *Kerbals screaming in background*\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"daniel l.","CreatedById":57763,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-17T23:50:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHow about making it work in orbit\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Drew Kerman","CreatedById":103177,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-17T23:55:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022daniel l.\u0022 data-cite=\u0022daniel l.\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EHow about making it work in orbit\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003Ethat makes no sense at all\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ximrm","CreatedById":111063,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-05-30T08:52:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWell, the whole anti grav. chamber was just a test for later mods that would allow artificial gravity in walkable IVAs...so there\u0027s a bit of a purpose there. But that mod will most likely not happen. Not because it wouldn\u0027t be possible but KSP isn\u0027t a priority in both our lives now.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHowever, I\u0027ll ask Tuareg if he\u0027ll update the mod. I had no involvement in this, so it\u0027s solely up to him.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}